erpt_area": {"text": "最近通关了某个银河城游戏，发现网友的许多批评都集中在「游戏没有受击保护」这一点上。我仔细想了想，似乎在银河城游戏，横板过关游戏等等类型中，确实大部分游戏都有「角色受到伤害之后一段时间内无敌」这样的设定。但这是为什么？毕竟 3D 游戏中就几乎不存在这种设定。 我个人的理解是，相比于 3D 游戏，2D 游戏相对更强调玩家在有限的 2D 空间内精确运动，因此早期 2D 游戏通常会引入碰撞伤害这类设定以逼迫玩家在空间里动起来。而在这种情况下，如果不加入受击保护的话，主角很有可能会被连续的碰撞伤害直接多次判定给秒杀。 且 2D 游戏或多或少会存在一些平台跳跃要素，一旦玩家跌入陷阱，那就需要重置位置和摄像机，而在重制之后如果没有受击保护，那就容易出现「跌入陷阱 - 重置 - 挨打 - 跌入陷阱 -…」这样的循环。 问题抛砖引玉，看看各位的理解"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-548cb378792f64ff36f04dd670701729_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661836585"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ipsyf0teUgrMeEAMaCTEwOTM1MjY2OCC5t920BjAAOC5ALnIJNjYxODM2NTg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1721668732.885394", "card_id": "Q_661648088", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你们下定决心并努力减肥的的动力都是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-68d7cac16eb634ff149bb23c9de2254d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661648088"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ipsyf0teUgrMeEAMaCTEwOTMxMDcyOSCZptK0BjAAOENAL3IJNjYxNjQ4MDg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1721668732.885762", "card_id": "Q_605694733", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 783}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "离职后，你一般怎么退出工作群？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e3de3b8d772a05d5cfcbf2ad1f8a1dc5_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "